<C>__{shifu}
<D>__{you did?!}
<A>__{shifu smiles and shakes his head in disbelief.}
<C>__{shifu }
<D>__{wow. it is as oogway foretold you are the dragon warrior. you have brought peace to this valley. and to me. thank you. thank you, po. thank you...}
