<D>__{if you can.}
<A>__{po nods reverently as shifu closes his eyes again. master and pupil lie next to each other. the camera pulls up and back away from them. po tries to remain still, but it's hard. he's about to say something, but he stops himself. he fidgets for a beat, then can't control himself any longer.}
